title: Gold Coast photo essay - interview with Kaz Inoue
text:
Gold Coast photo essay - interview with Kaz Inoue Christina Pfeiffer | 6th Jul 2015 5:14 PM Christina Pfeiffer Gold Coast. Photo: Kaz Inoue Popular Stories Local Real Estate Cars For Sale 
Queensland is full of fantastic photographers. I recently bumped into Kaz Inoue, who moved to the Gold Coast and was invited by Tourism and Events Queensland to be a guest curator of their Instagram account back in2013. 
Kaz's own Instagram account is inspirational. 
Her job at Currumbin Wildlife Sanctuary allows her do exciting things like hosting instameets and her photos were shown in Glasgow, during the Commonwealth Games last year. 
You can see Kaz's photos of Queensland and find out more about how Queensland has motivated her photography.
